00:09:15.972 --> 00:09:17.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[man] Okay, hold it...

140
00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:21.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[woman 1] Huh? Where'd he come from?
-[woman 2] I don't know...

141
00:09:21.478 --> 00:09:23.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He really thrives
on this stuff.

142
00:09:23.605 --> 00:09:25.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So does Origami Cyclone.

143
00:09:25.607 --> 00:09:27.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, there. Are we
almost done here?

144
00:09:28.026 --> 00:09:30.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Joubert] Yeah, it's late.
We've got to move on to the next location.

145
00:09:31.237 --> 00:09:32.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tiger] What?! There's more?

146
00:09:33.198 --> 00:09:35.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
One more, the Fortress
Tower Building.

147
00:09:36.159 --> 00:09:39.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The sponsor wants to get in some
free publicity for its new landmark.

148
00:09:43.875 --> 00:09:45.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah! Look at that!

149
00:09:48.755 --> 00:09:50.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Joubert] Come on, let's keep moving.

150
00:09:53.093 --> 00:09:55.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Tiger] Hey, wait!
Don't you wanna get a shot of this?

151
00:09:56.346 --> 00:09:58.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Look! It's Mr.
Legend!

152
00:10:00.016 --> 00:10:01.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh!

153
00:10:02.769 --> 00:10:04.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
There's something
wrong with it.

154
00:10:10.401 --> 00:10:13.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, is it okay
to get on?

155
00:10:13.947 --> 00:10:16.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yeah. I
just fixed it.

156
00:10:16.866 --> 00:10:19.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Fixed it? I thought this
place was brand new.

157
00:10:20.245 --> 00:10:24.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It wasn't anything big.
I was just greasing the cables.

158
00:10:27.460 --> 00:10:30.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Joubert] Well... we're waiting. Let's go.

159
00:10:30.296 --> 00:10:32.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tiger] Uhh. You sure it's safe?

160
00:10:32.173 --> 00:10:33.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Would you just get on?

161
00:10:37.971 --> 00:10:39.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm telling you, it's him!
It's Barnaby!

162
00:10:40.890 --> 00:10:42.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[young girl] Oh my God, he's
gorgeous!

163
00:10:42.600 --> 00:10:43.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[young girl 2] Shut up! [giggling]

164
00:10:43.893 --> 00:10:46.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Uh, doesn't that make
your arm tired?

165
00:10:46.396 --> 00:10:47.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What do you mean?

166
00:10:47.981 --> 00:10:51.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
'Scuse me, I was just wondering if I could
shake your hand?

167
00:10:51.276 --> 00:10:53.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sure. I'm pleased
to meet you.

168
00:10:53.570 --> 00:10:55.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[waitress] Likewise! Thank you!

169
00:10:55.363 --> 00:10:56.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're not sick
of that?

170
00:10:56.739 --> 00:10:59.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not really. Comes with the territory.

171
00:11:01.870 --> 00:11:03.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So then...
nice view.

172
00:11:03.997 --> 00:11:05.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Oh yeah, it's
breathtaking.

173
00:11:05.540 --> 00:11:08.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[scoffs] What's that building there?

174
00:11:08.293 --> 00:11:10.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jeez, man, I don't know, why're you--

175
00:11:12.088 --> 00:11:14.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well now, let's see... which one?

176
00:11:14.883 --> 00:11:16.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Bunny] There.
-[Tiger] Oh, that's...

177
00:11:16.509 --> 00:11:18.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
just your... standard... building.

178
00:11:18.970 --> 00:11:20.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Bunny] What about that one?
-[Tiger] That would be [sighs]

179
00:11:20.972 --> 00:11:21.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
another building.

180
00:11:21.973 --> 00:11:24.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And you see that thing next to it?
That's a building too.

181
00:11:24.434 --> 00:11:25.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And so's that little one down there.

182
00:11:26.019 --> 00:11:28.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
In fact, most of these things you see
sticking up are buildings!

183
00:11:28.855 --> 00:11:30.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Will you please
knock it off?!

184
00:11:30.523 --> 00:11:31.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I thought it was
going well.

185
00:11:32.233 --> 00:11:34.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[alarm sounding]

186
00:11:34.736 --> 00:11:35.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[loudspeaker] <i>Attention all visitors,</i>

187
00:11:36.029 --> 00:11:38.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>the building's security alarm</i>
<i>has been activated.</i>

188
00:11:38.907 --> 00:11:40.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Great.
-[loudspeaker] <i>Remain calm</i>

189
00:11:40.408 --> 00:11:41.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>-and await instructions</i>
-[official] Follow me!

190
00:11:41.993 --> 00:11:43.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>-from our security personnel.</i>
-Please, everyone!

191
00:11:43.369 --> 00:11:44.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We need to evacuate this floor!

192
00:11:44.871 --> 00:11:46.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What's this all
about? A fire?

193
00:11:46.539 --> 00:11:47.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Uh, well...
-[Joubert] It's okay,

194
00:11:48.082 --> 00:11:50.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
they're Barnaby and Wild Tiger.

195
00:11:50.376 --> 00:11:51.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You know, Hero TV?

196
00:11:52.170 --> 00:11:54.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh. Well, in that case, okay.

197
00:11:54.505 --> 00:11:56.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Just between you and me,
we got a bomb threat.

198
00:11:56.716 --> 00:11:58.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What?
-Where's the bomb?

199
00:11:58.635 --> 00:12:00.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[official] They didn't say.
We're still searching for it.

200
00:12:02.680 --> 00:12:04.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It could be some sort of
prank, I guess...

201
00:12:05.016 --> 00:12:07.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Were any demands made by
the perpetrator?

202
00:12:07.810 --> 00:12:09.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[official] No, not that I'm aware of.

203
00:12:10.104 --> 00:12:11.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It might be
a prank...

204
00:12:13.566 --> 00:12:15.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I was just greasing the
cables.

205
00:12:15.860 --> 00:12:17.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps] Be right back!

206
00:12:18.196 --> 00:12:20.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, where the
hell are you going?!

207
00:12:20.156 --> 00:12:21.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tiger] Just checkin' somethin' out!

208
00:12:21.741 --> 00:12:23.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[woman]
<i>A bomb, did you hear??</i>

209
00:12:24.702 --> 00:12:27.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Bunny] It's all right, everybody.
It's just a prank, from the looks of it.

210
00:12:28.248 --> 00:12:30.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But they want us out, just to be safe.

211
00:12:30.375 --> 00:12:32.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just think of it as a fire drill.

212
00:12:36.089 --> 00:12:37.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

213
00:12:53.022 --> 00:12:53.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasping]

214
00:12:54.941 --> 00:12:56.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Damn!

215
00:12:56.567 --> 00:12:57.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's huge! That thing...

216
00:12:58.069 --> 00:12:59.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
could flatten this
whole building!

217
00:13:05.868 --> 00:13:07.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
All right, people, this way!
This way!

218
00:13:07.996 --> 00:13:11.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's all right, no need
to panic, everyone stay calm!

219
00:13:11.624 --> 00:13:14.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Single file down the
stairs, nice and easy!

220
00:13:15.545 --> 00:13:18.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Joubert] <i>The hero showing he's a hero</i>
<i>even when he's out of costume.</i>

221
00:13:19.007 --> 00:13:20.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>This footage is golden!</i>

222
00:13:20.591 --> 00:13:22.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[producer] Uh, Miss Joubert?

223
00:13:22.719 --> 00:13:24.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't you think we should
maybe get out of here, too?

224
00:13:25.013 --> 00:13:28.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You crazy? Something finally happens
and you wanna--

225
00:13:29.392 --> 00:13:30.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hey--
-What?

226
00:13:31.936 --> 00:13:35.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-How much time we got?
-[Joubert] So, it really is a bomb.

227
00:13:36.566 --> 00:13:37.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let's go.

228
00:13:38.151 --> 00:13:39.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

229
00:13:39.694 --> 00:13:42.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You! You're both coming with me.

230
00:13:42.447 --> 00:13:44.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We stick to them like glue.

231
00:13:44.615 --> 00:13:46.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't just stand
there, come on!

232
00:13:47.160 --> 00:13:48.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You've got to leave
like everyone else.

233
00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:50.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? No way.

234
00:13:50.538 --> 00:13:53.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Listen, buddy, I've got a show to
run here, whether you like it or n--

235
00:13:53.333 --> 00:13:54.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're not runnin'
this show!

236
00:13:54.876 --> 00:13:55.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

237
00:13:55.835 --> 00:13:58.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This isn't a game anymore Agnes,
it's the real deal.

238
00:13:58.713 --> 00:14:00.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Look, if you want us to be heroes,

239
00:14:00.256 --> 00:14:02.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you gotta get out of the way
and let us do our job!

240
00:14:03.092 --> 00:14:05.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And that job's defending
the people of this city

241
00:14:05.303 --> 00:14:07.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and that means everyone.

242
00:14:07.722 --> 00:14:09.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Including you
and your crew.

243
00:14:14.437 --> 00:14:17.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Whoa, man. That was a
cool speech he made, right?

244
00:14:17.565 --> 00:14:18.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh? Whatever!

245
00:14:19.609 --> 00:14:21.986 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're forgetting, we've got
a job to do, too.

246
00:14:22.070 --> 00:14:25.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, don't worry. The old man can
shoot your footage for you.

247
00:14:25.406 --> 00:14:26.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh??

248
00:14:27.116 --> 00:14:28.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jerk!

249
00:14:30.620 --> 00:14:32.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm gonna have to direct this shoot
from the van,

250
00:14:32.497 --> 00:14:34.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
bring it around front right now!

251
00:14:36.417 --> 00:14:37.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>We go now to Fortress Tower,</i>

252
00:14:37.877 --> 00:14:40.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>where officials have confirmed</i>
<i>that a bomb threat was received</i>

253
00:14:40.338 --> 00:14:41.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>at 7:15 this evening.</i>

254
00:14:42.298 --> 00:14:44.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>...forcing them to evacuate</i>
<i>hundreds of visitors</i>

255
00:14:44.467 --> 00:14:45.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>from the brand-new building...</i>

256
00:14:45.676 --> 00:14:49.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>The latest word from here is that everyone</i>
<i>has been evacuated safely,</i>

257
00:14:49.430 --> 00:14:52.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>largely through the efforts of</i>
<i>the world-famous Heroes,</i>

258
00:14:52.225 --> 00:14:54.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>who arrived quickly on</i>
<i>the scene.</i>

259
00:14:57.772 --> 00:15:00.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Authorities don't yet know</i>
<i>who is behind the bomb threat</i>

260
00:15:00.566 --> 00:15:03.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>or why the Fortress Tower building</i>
<i>has been targeted.</i>

261
00:15:03.528 --> 00:15:06.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>They don't even know yet</i>
<i>whether there really is a bomb,</i>

262
00:15:06.155 --> 00:15:08.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>but meanwhile,</i>
<i>they're taking every precaution.</i>

263
00:15:08.616 --> 00:15:11.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Okay, let's get this
party started.

264
00:15:13.579 --> 00:15:16.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Can't wait to see if they'll pull
this off. [chuckling]

265
00:15:19.752 --> 00:15:22.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tiger] So, any ideas, Bunny?

266
00:15:26.342 --> 00:15:29.262 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
While we're waiting, tell our viewers
what hair product you use!

267
00:15:29.762 --> 00:15:32.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What made you think that
the bomb was here, anyway?

268
00:15:32.348 --> 00:15:34.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Tiger] Oh, it just seemed strange that
they were still working

269
00:15:34.434 --> 00:15:36.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
on the elevator
after the building had opened.

270
00:15:36.727 --> 00:15:37.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Is that all?

271
00:15:37.812 --> 00:15:39.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You saw that guy. That workman.

272
00:15:39.981 --> 00:15:42.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He was way too clean to have been
greasing cables all day.

273
00:15:43.067 --> 00:15:44.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
His clothes were spotless.

274
00:15:44.444 --> 00:15:47.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Years and years of honing your skills
have paid off, I see.

275
00:15:47.405 --> 00:15:50.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[gasps] Hey, it hasn't been
that many years, okay?!

276
00:15:50.575 --> 00:15:52.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So, seriously,
you got a plan?

277
00:15:52.869 --> 00:15:54.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, to be careful.

278
00:15:54.287 --> 00:15:56.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're lucky you didn't set it off
when you barged in here.

279
00:15:57.123 --> 00:15:58.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[giggles]

280
00:15:58.249 --> 00:16:01.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Fortunately, I've had some experience
with devices like this.

281
00:16:02.170 --> 00:16:04.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're kidding me.
